    "title": "Career Opportunity Software Engineer at Samsung R&D India Ventures Solutions",
    "description": "Samsung R&D India Ventures Solutions, one of India's leading organizations, is hiring a Software Engineer for our Mysuru operations. We offer a competitive salary package along with world-class benefits.\n\nAbout Samsung R&D India Ventures Solutions:\nSamsung R&D India Ventures Solutions is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Write clean, maintainable, and well-documented code\n• Collaborate with cross-functional teams including product, design, and QA\n• Deploy and manage applications on cloud platforms like AWS, Azure, or GCP\n• Participate in code reviews and contribute to technical discussions\n• Mentor junior developers and conduct knowledge-sharing sessions\n• Participate in on-call rotation for production support\n• Write and execute unit tests and integration tests\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• Post Graduate Diploma in relevant field\n• 1-3 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in AWS\n• Proficiency in Git\n• Proficiency in Machine Learning\n• Proficiency in Node.js\n• Proficiency in Microservices\n• Proficiency in Go\n• Proficiency in React\n• Proficiency in Java\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Recognition and rewards programs\n• Learning & development budget\n• Mobile and internet reimbursement\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Salary Range: 4 LPA - 9 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Mysuru, Karnataka, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Samsung R&D India Ventures Solutions!",
